text: Demigender describes non-binary identities of someone experiencing partial connection to certain gender. Individuals that identify as demigender may identify as partially a girl (demigirl) or boy (demiboy), and this could also be a combination of genders. ==Flags== File:Deminonbinary flag.svg|Demigender, demienby or deminonbinary flag File:Demiboy Flag.svg|Demiboy flag File:Demigirl Flag.svg|Demigirl flag File:Demifluid.png|Demifluid (demigenderfluid) flag File:Demiandrogyne Flag.png|Demiandrogyne flag == References == Category:Non-binary gender
title: Demigender
